336
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,180
and

337
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:46,940
didn't want him to wake up.

338
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:50,620
Well...

339
00:20:51,620 --> 00:20:53,220
If nothing else,

340
00:20:53,220 --> 00:20:54,140
