341
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:56,020
As for the deed,

342
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:57,580
you can send it to Huanxi Clinic

343
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:58,660
in Guiyi District.

344
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:01,060
