384
00:23:12,100 --> 00:23:13,820
You destroyed the cult.

385
00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:16,420
I just wanted to get
Madam Wang's deed back.

386
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:17,900
Besides,

387
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:20,620
